title: Solana Shooter 'Nyan Heroes' Boosts Airdrop Rewards in Epic Games Demo
description: Starting March 30, gamers can earn double the MEOW points in Nyan Heroes on PC for a share of the upcoming NYAN token airdrop on Solana.

title: Cat-themed token on Solana soar over 120% in 24 hours
description: MEW managed to soar even after airdropping 5% of its total supply to BONK and WIF holders, in its quest to start 'cat season.'
